Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:11.05,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}翻译：絆咲  Miya　校对：千叶命　后期：volence／阿爽/whwdlxy9416
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:54.53,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰かのためなら悪くはないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:01:00.37,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}理由らしいものは今日も　…見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:05.89,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曖昧なリアル　点と点をつなぐ光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:12.63,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}消えそうな夢を　そっと握りしめてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:22.26,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}僕たちの声が  君の癒やせない傷痕に届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:27.86,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ナガレテク　雲の速さへと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:33.88,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}置いてかれないように叫ぶ　今日のエチュード
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:41.22,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}カナエタイ　静かな絶望の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:46.13,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}新しい　はじまりへのページ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.87,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その手をとって　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.68,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君が望むから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.14,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}どこまでも行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:54.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}若是为了谁  这无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:01:00.37,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天依然没看见像样的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:05.89,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暧昧交织的现实  点点相连的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:12.63,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尝试着握住那转眼即逝的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:22.26,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我们的声音  若能传达到你那无法治愈的伤痕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:27.86,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}宛如流云的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:33.88,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为了不再置之不理  放声唱出今天的练习曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:41.22,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}渴望着那寂静的绝望的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:46.13,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是通向全新伊始的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.87,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}牵住你的手  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.68,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}正如你所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.14,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一路向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:12.08,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}路地裏には暗い暗い灯り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:16.56,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}そこに集う羽虫達のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:20.77,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}もがく僕らは cry cry 共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:25.25,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}秘めた思いをくすぶらせてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:29.92,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}「何をすればいい」　それがわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:34.27,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無限の意味恐れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:38.58,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}しびれ切らした両の足が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.80,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}立ち上がれとせがんでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:51.27,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}全て運命だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.41,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}神の落書きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.89,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}丸めて捨てるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.95,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}たったひとつの冴えたやり方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:04.13,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}いつも胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:10.19,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}夜明け　睨みつけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:12.08,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}小巷里昏暗的灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:16.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}引得小飞虫纷纷聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:20.77,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我们心急如焚一同哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:25.25,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}煽起深藏心中的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:29.92,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我不知该何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:34.27,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}无限的意义使我畏缩不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:38.58,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}面对那失去知觉的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.80,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我央求道  快快站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:51.27,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}一切都是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只是神轻描淡写的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.89,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}看我把它揉成一团一并扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.95,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}唯一行之有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:04.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}就是谨记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:10.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}怒视拂晓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酱油拉面一碗做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点酱油拉面的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味噌拉面也好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等鸣海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…明老板？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说要通宵我实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海  还记得白天那位客人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在靠边的啤酒箱上的那位  带着墨镜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来好像拉面也没吃几口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是…今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盐味拉面  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味噌拉面  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葱味拉面  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是对我的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找上门的麻烦我奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用新作品让他尝尝苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了明老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把菜刀拿开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了就快来准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从改良汤头开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岛同学没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不…也不能说没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经连续三天熬夜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能和我换班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过帮忙做汤头的话还是要让你来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站…站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  鸣海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老板…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什…什么打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚洗完澡  很正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在吵什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可没啥可偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老板？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠胸布被偷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即处以绞刑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就狠狠地揍他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位考虑问题怎么那么暴力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岛中将  你这还算新人NEET吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就不是NEET…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过几年这里就会成为你的归处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是显而易见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸拉面是我们NEET的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所谓的圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷走这里的老大明老板的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无理之极  绝不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错  能赊账的只有这家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心话是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  来这么多人是要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于小偷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不和我们商量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事谁会开口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的缠胸布被偷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就要靠无论是洗黑钱还是缠胸布大盗事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能顺利解决的NEET侦探团集合全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别集合全力来妨碍我做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  明老板今天缠胸布的颜色变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第四次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可能是跟踪狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很了解跟踪狂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住女朋友家里的时候  遇到过几次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陪酒店或是特殊服务的店也经常…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可是拉面店  不是陪酒的也不是特殊服务的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  现在缠胸布被偷是事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至于用剩下的门帘布顶替缠胸布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是跟踪狂么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老板  最近有没有接到无声电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}那不太可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信箱里有被塞进什么东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}那个也太夸张了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有感觉到背后有人跟着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}再怎么也不会做到那份上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来错不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  明老板？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  老板  很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有求与我的一天终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  变大的只有嘴上功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛  放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点都没成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有好好吃东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我悄悄地多加了肉给你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙也有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人都有适合自己的体型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄取蛋白质就会膨胀起来这种简单的想法不可取
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明老板去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老板昨晚以前缠胸布被偷在是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周四  那个墨镜男来点了盐味拉面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨镜男是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次来都点不同的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本不怎么动筷子就走的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周四墨镜男来  缠胸布失窃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天墨镜男来  缠胸布也失窃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨镜男就是小偷么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我觉得那不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体型差别太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是共犯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝  摄像机的录像呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没拍到？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少没拍到可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是事实  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何既然是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次墨镜男出现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能再次盗窃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人之血久违地沸腾起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手都痒痒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加强店面周边的防卫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女孩们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想让我的店倒闭么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的事  毕竟她并没有正式委托我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下嘛  还是让他们调查下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  委托爱丽丝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会把缠胸布拿去闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定每天都会闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡前醒来都闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定大街上边走边闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我委托你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我委托你可以了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哲负责打听客人和可疑人物的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿宏负责在车站附近收集情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐负责分析摄像机以及强化保安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像往常一样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次入侵者出现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没起作用的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了帮老板打杂之外还能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我回去咯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实店里的客人也看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是像幽灵一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视摄像机方面呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可谓神出鬼没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  吃点拉面重整旗鼓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡麻拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡麻辣面  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然出了这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以彩夏在抓到犯人之前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我无论如何都要去照看温室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没法来打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过藤岛同学还是担心一下自己比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是一副快挂掉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道  跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在附近再找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我向爱丽丝和明老板报告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏哥刚才联系我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试喝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道不怎么好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉一股海藻味  不像拉面的汤底了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这锅汤底也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜那位客人可能想吃老爸的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这锅汤底是…你父亲的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿而已  模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸也没想过我会继承这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没问过配料表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直在叛逆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计他都放弃这家店和我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是入侵者今晚出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒计划已经完备了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且老板家的保安也进行了强化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝  关于这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个玄关的锁绝对不可以动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么老式的锁只要想撬谁都能撬开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了强化保安只能将它换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老板无论如何都不同意换
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨镜男和窃贼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有拒绝更换旧锁的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白些什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门锁这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松警戒  引诱犯人行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时我会动员仅有的一点勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏出这座堡垒  亲自用双手去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了把真相化为事实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏哥哲哥已就位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也尽快回到岗位上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…我要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岛中将负责室内的警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人要是出现了就用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是诱饵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你再逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  藤岛中将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井均特制闪光弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是在扰邻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉迷于你的缠胸布气味的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是我这个侦探的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿宏  他的身份是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村富雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIS  ANGELICA的开发部部长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  是个大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIS  ANGELICA是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是知名女性内衣制造商
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎是那里的设计师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村富雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要偷缠胸布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能忍受她使用缠胸布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠胸布根本就不是内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真理的探求者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我光是用看的就能知道女性内衣的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光用看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是被上帝选中的人才拥有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的内衣可以衬托女性的身段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性的胴体可以让内衣闪亮发光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造就这究极之美正是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掌握了你的胸围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下胸围70上胸围95的G罩杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在我们业界是被称为泰姬玛哈陵般的奇迹形状的人间至宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种奇迹般的胸竟然被缠胸布束缚住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是亵渎上帝的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了让你开窍连照片都发你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须穿戴我这个艺术家所设计的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你的遗言是不是就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  我没打算阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认为在得知事件真相后再动手也不迟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村富雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于你侵入时所见到的一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我换个问法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是如何侵入这间屋子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因为玄关的锁就是开着的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明上锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁是开着的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每天都监视着这间屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而某天他看见某个人光明正大地打开玄关的门进入屋内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就从没有上锁的门潜入这间屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他认为那个人是这间房子的住户
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们则认为他是你的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好说明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  你拒绝了换门锁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的选择是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…可是事到如今才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…明老板也在等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等令尊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要是不狠狠揍他一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这气就没地方消啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去店里说不定就能找到答案哦  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人有两人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都是单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前放跑的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后突破我们重重包围网的墨镜男子是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花田胜  老板的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她爸爸是来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在老板应该在聆听生者的话语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没想像中好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹是来嘲笑我的拉面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一声不吭地就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是回来了也至少说句话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次回来的时候让我尝尝你的冰激凌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  不管怎么想他都是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你的动态视力只对女性有效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这只是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能避开监控摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被察觉的情况下掌握拍摄范围并快速通过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到这点的绝非凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再综合宏哥的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说他在特殊机关接受过训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还做了整容手术回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么明老板会察觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是亲生女儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要否定就拿别的假设推翻我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今早在店里发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你真的不管什么尺寸都看得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是飞机场也没问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  根据情况今天倒不是不能放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说爱丽丝那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在愚弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我像老板那样长肉来配合这个尺寸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是挂在门上…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个又恶劣又不知羞耻又无礼的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说这是误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  爱丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}NEET侦探事务所  爱丽丝小姐收
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四代举办的活动上帮忙的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.56,0:23:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能胜任候选负责人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了危险却又不可思议的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
